"""v2-S04 iter 8 step 3 — 4-panel before/after TPS overlays per subject.

Per the new protocol (2026-04-29):
  Panel 1: HCR 488 raw (z-MIP, green colormap) + GFP+ ROI contours (white).
  Panel 2: GFP+ landmark contours (green) + GFP+ other contours (white)
           + CZ landmark contours (red) + CZ other contours (yellow), BEFORE TPS.
  Panel 3: same color scheme as Panel 2 but CZ ROIs AFTER TPS transformation.
  Panel 4: HCR 488 (green) + CZ ROIs after TPS overlaid (red landmarks, yellow others).

Coordinate frame: HCR µm dst-space grid at 2 µm, viewport = bbox(landmark
src + dst) + 10 % margin. CZ ROIs in src-space are sampled via inverse-LP;
post-TPS CZ ROIs use inverse-TPS (fit from gfp→cz_warp anchors) ∘ inverse-LP.
"""
